                'content'          => '<h2>Transfer Certificate – Sample Format</h2><p>Below is the official format of the Transfer Certificate (TC) issued by HS Global Academy. This is for reference purposes only.</p><div style="border:2px solid #000; padding:30px; max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; font-family:serif;"><div style="text-align:center;"><h3 style="margin-bottom:0;">HS GLOBAL ACADEMY</h3><p style="margin-top:0;">Affiliated to CBSE, New Delhi | Affiliation No: XXXXXX</p><p>School Address Line 1, City, State – PIN</p><hr style="border-color:#000;"><h3 style="letter-spacing:4px;">TRANSFER CERTIFICATE</h3></div><p><strong>TC No.:</strong> _______________ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Date:</strong> _______________</p><p><strong>Admission No.:</strong> _______________ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>UID:</strong> _______________</p><hr><p>This is to certify that <strong>____________________________</strong>, Son / Daughter of <strong>Shri / Smt. ____________________________</strong>, Date of Birth: <strong>_______________</strong>, was a bonafide student of this school.</p><table style="width:100%;"><tr><td><strong>Date of Admission:</strong> _____________</td><td><strong>Class at Admission:</strong> __________</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Date of Leaving:</strong> _____________</td><td><strong>Class Last Attended:</strong> __________</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Academic Year:</strong> _____________</td><td><strong>Result:</strong> Passed / Promoted to Class _______</td></tr></table><p><strong>Conduct:</strong> _______________ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Games / Sports Participated:</strong> _______________</p><p><strong>Reason for Leaving:</strong> _______________</p><p><strong>Remarks (if any):</strong> _______________</p><br><table style="width:100%;"><tr><td style="text-align:center;"><strong>_________________________</strong><br>Class Teacher</td><td style="text-align:center;"><strong>_________________________</strong><br>Principal</td></tr></table><br><p style="text-align:center;">(School Seal)</p></div><h3>Important Information</h3><ul><li>The actual TC is printed on the <strong>school\'s official letterhead</strong> with security features.</li><li>A TC is issued only after <strong>full clearance of all dues</strong> and return of school property.</li><li>The TC is a <strong>legal document</strong> — any tampering or falsification is punishable under applicable laws.</li><li>For duplicate TC, submit a written application along with an <strong>affidavit</strong> and ₹500 fee.</li></ul>',
